drizzle of wine and cheese sauce.

10:52.892 --> 10:56.133
With the cheese literally
coming out the sides. Look at that.

10:56.293 --> 10:57.933
I know!

10:58.093 --> 11:00.493
Who likes cheese balls?
I love cheese balls.

11:00.653 --> 11:02.533
Cheese balls!

11:02.693 --> 11:05.734
Some Parmigiano
or pecorino cheese.

11:07.494 --> 11:09.854
With a lot of Swiss cheese.

11:12.414 --> 11:15.894
Take a piece of provolone cheese

11:16.054 --> 11:19.455
and nest it in the meatball.

11:19.615 --> 11:21.175
Yeah.

11:21.335 --> 11:22.655
How cute is that?

11:22.815 --> 11:29.415
And hello, the cheese,
feta, baby, feta. Whoo!

11:29.576 --> 11:32.376
You need a fair amount
of cheese on top.

11:33.496 --> 11:35.496
- Double the cheese!
