17:47.127 --> 17:49.967
Robocallers can pretend to be
calling from your area,

17:50.127 --> 17:52.128
increasing the chance
that you will pick up.

17:52.288 --> 17:54.488
And individual scammers can
even pretend to be

17:54.648 --> 17:57.688
someone that you know,
